# MyBatis-Plus 使用规则

## 实体类规范

### 基本注解
```java
@Data
@TableName("user")
public class User {
    @TableId(type = IdType.AUTO)
    private Long id;
    
    private String username;
    
    private String email;
    
    @TableField(fill = FieldFill.INSERT)
    private LocalDateTime createTime;
    
    @TableField(fill = FieldFill.INSERT_UPDATE)
    private LocalDateTime updateTime;
    
    @TableLogic
    private Integer deleted;
}
```

### 常用注解说明
- `@TableName`: 指定表名
- `@TableId`: 主键，`IdType.AUTO` 自增，`IdType.ASSIGN_ID` 雪花算法
- `@TableField`: 字段映射
- `@TableLogic`: 逻辑删除字段

## Mapper 接口规范

### 继承 BaseMapper
```java
@Mapper
public interface UserMapper extends BaseMapper<User> {
    // 继承 BaseMapper 后自动拥有 CRUD 方法
    
    // 自定义复杂查询
    IPage<User> selectUserPage(IPage<User> page, @Param("keyword") String keyword);
    
    // 自定义统计查询
    Long countByStatus(@Param("status") Integer status);
}
```

## Service 层规范

### 继承 IService
```java
public interface UserService extends IService<User> {
    // 继承 IService 后自动拥有批量操作方法
    
    // 自定义业务方法
    PageResult<UserVO> listUsers(Integer pageNum, Integer pageSize, String keyword);
}
```

### 实现类继承 ServiceImpl
```java
@Service
@RequiredArgsConstructor
public class UserServiceImpl extends ServiceImpl<UserMapper, User> implements UserService {
    
    @Override
    public PageResult<UserVO> listUsers(Integer pageNum, Integer pageSize, String keyword) {
        Page<User> page = new Page<>(pageNum, pageSize);
        LambdaQueryWrapper<User> wrapper = new LambdaQueryWrapper<>();
        wrapper.like(StringUtils.isNotBlank(keyword), User::getUsername, keyword)
               .orderByDesc(User::getCreateTime);
        
        Page<User> result = this.page(page, wrapper);
        return new PageResult<>(result.getRecords(), result.getTotal(), pageNum, pageSize);
    }
}
```

## 条件构造器使用

### LambdaQueryWrapper（推荐）
```java
LambdaQueryWrapper<User> wrapper = new LambdaQueryWrapper<>();

// 等于
wrapper.eq(User::getStatus, 1);

// 模糊查询
wrapper.like(User::getUsername, "张");

// 范围查询
wrapper.between(User::getAge, 18, 60);

// 多条件 OR
wrapper.eq(User::getStatus, 1)
       .or()
       .eq(User::getRole, "admin");

// 排序
wrapper.orderByDesc(User::getCreateTime);

// 查询指定字段
wrapper.select(User::getId, User::getUsername);

List<User> users = userMapper.selectList(wrapper);
```

### 常用条件方法
- `eq`: 等于 =
- `ne`: 不等于 !=
- `gt`: 大于 >
- `ge`: 大于等于 >=
- `lt`: 小于 <
- `le`: 小于等于 <=
- `like`: 模糊查询 LIKE
- `in`: IN 查询
- `between`: BETWEEN 查询
- `isNull`: IS NULL
- `isNotNull`: IS NOT NULL
- `orderByAsc`: 升序排序
- `orderByDesc`: 降序排序

## 分页查询

```java
// Controller
@GetMapping
public Result<PageResult<UserVO>> list(
    @RequestParam(defaultValue = "1") Integer pageNum,
    @RequestParam(defaultValue = "10") Integer pageSize) {
    return Result.success(userService.listUsers(pageNum, pageSize));
}

// Service
public PageResult<UserVO> listUsers(Integer pageNum, Integer pageSize) {
    Page<User> page = new Page<>(pageNum, pageSize);
    Page<User> result = this.page(page);
    
    List<UserVO> voList = result.getRecords().stream()
            .map(this::convertToVO)
            .collect(Collectors.toList());
    
    return new PageResult<>(voList, result.getTotal(), pageNum, pageSize);
}
```

## 批量操作

### 批量插入
```java
List<User> users = new ArrayList<>();
// ... 添加用户
userService.saveBatch(users);
```

### 批量更新
```java
List<User> users = userMapper.selectList(null);
users.forEach(user -> user.setStatus(1));
userService.updateBatchById(users);
```

### 批量删除
```java
List<Long> ids = Arrays.asList(1L, 2L, 3L);
userService.removeByIds(ids);
```

## 逻辑删除配置

### application.yml
```yaml
mybatis-plus:
  global-config:
    db-config:
      logic-delete-field: deleted
      logic-delete-value: 1
      logic-not-delete-value: 0
```

### 实体类
```java
@TableLogic
private Integer deleted;
```

使用逻辑删除后，删除操作会自动变为更新操作。

## 自动填充

### 配置自动填充处理器
```java
@Component
public class MyMetaObjectHandler implements MetaObjectHandler {
    
    @Override
    public void insertFill(MetaObject metaObject) {
        this.strictInsertFill(metaObject, "createTime", LocalDateTime.class, LocalDateTime.now());
        this.strictInsertFill(metaObject, "updateTime", LocalDateTime.class, LocalDateTime.now());
    }
    
    @Override
    public void updateFill(MetaObject metaObject) {
        this.strictUpdateFill(metaObject, "updateTime", LocalDateTime.class, LocalDateTime.now());
    }
}
```

### 实体类标注
```java
@TableField(fill = FieldFill.INSERT)
private LocalDateTime createTime;

@TableField(fill = FieldFill.INSERT_UPDATE)
private LocalDateTime updateTime;
```

## 代码生成器

```java
public class CodeGenerator {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        FastAutoGenerator.create("jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/db", "root", "password")
                .globalConfig(builder -> {
                    builder.author("author")
                           .outputDir(System.getProperty("user.dir") + "/src/main/java");
                })
                .packageConfig(builder -> {
                    builder.parent("com.company.project")
                           .entity("entity")
                           .mapper("mapper")
                           .service("service")
                           .serviceImpl("service.impl")
                           .controller("controller");
                })
                .strategyConfig(builder -> {
                    builder.addInclude("user", "order")
                           .entityBuilder()
                           .enableLombok()
                           .enableTableFieldAnnotation()
                           .logicDeleteColumnName("deleted")
                           .addTableFills(new Column("create_time", FieldFill.INSERT))
                           .addTableFills(new Column("update_time", FieldFill.INSERT_UPDATE));
                })
                .execute();
    }
}
```

## 常用查询示例

### 单条查询
```java
// 根据 ID 查询
User user = userMapper.selectById(1L);

// 根据条件查询一条
LambdaQueryWrapper<User> wrapper = new LambdaQueryWrapper<>();
wrapper.eq(User::getUsername, "admin");
User user = userMapper.selectOne(wrapper);
```

### 列表查询
```java
// 查询所有
List<User> users = userMapper.selectList(null);

// 条件查询
LambdaQueryWrapper<User> wrapper = new LambdaQueryWrapper<>();
wrapper.eq(User::getStatus, 1);
List<User> users = userMapper.selectList(wrapper);
```

### 统计查询
```java
// 统计总数
Long count = userMapper.selectCount(null);

// 条件统计
LambdaQueryWrapper<User> wrapper = new LambdaQueryWrapper<>();
wrapper.eq(User::getStatus, 1);
Long count = userMapper.selectCount(wrapper);
```

### 更新操作
```java
// 根据 ID 更新
User user = new User();
user.setId(1L);
user.setUsername("newName");
userMapper.updateById(user);

// 条件更新
LambdaUpdateWrapper<User> wrapper = new LambdaUpdateWrapper<>();
wrapper.eq(User::getId, 1L)
       .set(User::getStatus, 1);
userMapper.update(null, wrapper);
```

## 性能优化建议

1. **只查询需要的字段**
```java
wrapper.select(User::getId, User::getUsername);
```

2. **使用分页避免一次查询大量数据**
```java
Page<User> page = new Page<>(1, 10);
```

3. **批量操作使用 saveBatch/updateBatchById**
```java
userService.saveBatch(users, 1000); // 每批 1000 条
```

4. **避免 N+1 查询问题，使用关联查询**
```xml
<resultMap id="UserWithOrdersMap" type="User">
    <collection property="orders" ofType="Order" select="selectOrders"/>
</resultMap>
```

5. **合理使用索引，在常查询字段上建立索引**

## 最佳实践

1. **使用 LambdaQueryWrapper 避免硬编码字段名**
2. **复杂查询写 XML，简单查询用 Wrapper**
3. **使用逻辑删除而不是物理删除**
4. **统一使用 Service 层方法，避免直接调用 Mapper**
5. **分页查询使用 MyBatis-Plus 的 Page 对象**
6. **批量操作优先使用 saveBatch/updateBatchById**
7. **合理配置自动填充，减少重复代码**
